"\\end{bmatrix}\n"
"\\begin{bmatrix}\n"
"\\textbf k_0\\\\ \\textbf k_1 \\\\\\vdots \\\\\\textbf k_{n-1}\n"
"\\end{bmatrix}=\n"
"\\begin{bmatrix}\n"
"B_0 + A_0 u \\\\\n"
